Package org.firebirdsql.logging

Interface Logger

  • @Deprecated
public interface Logger
    Deprecated.
    will be removed in Jaybird 6 without replacement
    Logger is a facade to hide the logging implementation used from the rest of Jaybird.
    Author:
    David Jencks, Blas Rodriguez Somoza, Mark Rotteveel

      • warnDebug

        default void warnDebug​(java.lang.String message,
                       java.lang.Throwable t)
        Deprecated.
        Logs the message on warn with the throwable toString() and a note that the stacktrace is on debug. The message and the stacktrace of t are also logged on debug.
        Parameters:
        message - Message to log
        t - Throwable to log (toString() on warn and full stacktrace on debug)

      • errorDebug

        default void errorDebug​(java.lang.String message,
                        java.lang.Throwable t)
        Deprecated.
        Logs the message on error with the throwable toString() and a note that the stacktrace is on debug. The message and the stacktrace of t are also logged on debug.
        Parameters:
        message - Message to log
        t - Throwable to log (toString() on error and full stacktrace on debug)
